originalText.text: A fabulous principal who has carried the legacy of Ellen Lurie for 15 years, Ms Wanda Soto is retiring and she has done well. The school is a dynamic learning envirnment, multi-racial, mutli-lingual and fully inclusive. The parent and commiity engagement is strong and the purposeful intent of its namesake is well tended. It takes a village to raise our children. It happens here!
